item.more_critters.critter_fossil_1.desc: §7Appears to be a broken tusk from a mammal
item.more_critters.critter_fossil_10.des: §7Appears to be a well perserved fossil of an invertebrate. It is most likely an arthropod but doesn't fit in any of the arthropod families
item.more_critters.critter_fossil_2.desc: §7Appears to be the hand bones of a mammal with large claws
item.more_critters.critter_fossil_3.desc: §7Appears to be the tooth from a carnivore, analysis suggests it was a reptile
item.more_critters.critter_fossil_4.desc: §7Appears to be the tooth of a plant eating reptile, the size of this tooth suggests the animal was very large
item.more_critters.critter_fossil_5.desc: §7Appears to be a the tail bones of a large animal, at the tip is a large bulb
item.more_critters.critter_fossil_6.desc: §7Appears to be the skull and spine of an amphibian, what remains of it's teeth suggests it was a carnivore
item.more_critters.critter_fossil_7.desc: §7Appears to be the shell of a large arthropod. Microscopic pores on the shell indicates this creature lived on land
item.more_critters.critter_fossil_8.desc: §7Appears to be the remains of an ancient fish with an armored head. It also has six fins
item.more_critters.critter_fossil_9.desc: §7Appears to be the shell of a mollusk. The shell has an odd shape to it
§7Appears to be the bones of a flying creature, the eye sockets indicate it was nocturnal
§7Appears to be the remains of a small reptile with odd appendages on it's back
§7Appears to be the fossil of an invertebrate with a trunk like appendage and five eyes
item.more_critters.fungal_staff.descript: §7Hit an entity to give them the §4Imminent Death §7effect
§7Rare chance for the entity  to get stuck in §4Mori Shroom Roots
§7Right click to give yourself the §6Gift of Life §7effect
§7Shift and Right click to §6heal players and pets around you
